NK041(di)025:1: 'bru gsum kyis 'dod dgu mi zad nam mkha'i mdzod du brlabs la /
NK041(di)025:4: khams gsum srid par gnas pa yi //
NK041(di)025:6: gdug cing srog la rngam pa dang //
NK041(di)025:7: sha khrag zas la dga' ba rnams //
NK041(di)025:8: rang rang yid mthun 'dod dgu'i gter //
NK041(di)025:9: zag med bde ba'i tshim gyur nas //
NK041(di)025:10: gnod 'tshe gdug rtsub zhi gyur cig /
NK041(di)025:11: khyad par bdag dang sbyin bdag gi //
NK041(di)025:13: zas nor dpal la 'gong byed pa'i //
NK041(di)025:14: lan chags rkyen bgegs byed rnams la //
NK041(di)025:15: 'dod yon mi zad gter du bsngo //
NK041(di)025:16: dga' mgu yi rang tshim gyur nas //
NK041(di)025:17: zhi zhing byams pa'i sems ldan shog /
NK041(di)025:18: yul 'di'i snod dang bcud rnams la //
NK041(di)025:20: mi la 'tshe zhing phyugs la gnod //
NK041(di)025:23: glo bur lhag pa'i gdon bgegs tshogs //
NK041(di)025:24: gang dag ji snyed mchis pa la //
NK041(di)025:25: mi zad bde ba'i gter du bsngo //
NK041(di)025:26: 'di ltar gsur mchod khyad par can //
NK041(di)025:27: ngo bo bde chen ye shes la //
NK041(di)025:28: rnam pa 'dod dgu mi zad gter //
NK041(di)025:29: gang la bsngosa pa tshim gyur cig /
NK041(di)025:30: 'khrul ba'i sems kyi dbang song bas //
NK041(di)025:31: rtag tu gdung zhing mnar ba yi //
NK041(di)025:32: yid can ji snyed mchis rnams kyi //
NK041(di)025:33: yid la bde chen gter ldan shog /
NK041(di)025:34: byang chub sems kyi srog rnyed cing //
NK041(di)025:35: shes rab chen po'i mig thob nas //
NK041(di)025:36: rgyal ba'i sras kyi spyod pa la //
NK041(di)025:38: bdag dang spyin pa'i bdag po yi //
NK041(di)025:39: tshe rabs thog ma med pa nas //
NK041(di)025:40: bu lon lan chags sod gyur cig /
NK041(di)025:41: skye ba kun du bgegs med shog /
NK041(di)025:42: phral gyi rkyen bgegs byed rnams kyang //
NK041(di)025:43: sha mkhon sdig sgrib dag gyur nas //
NK041(di)025:44: deng nas byang chub snying po'i bar //
NK041(di)025:45: gnod tshe'i sbyor ba rgyun chad shog /
NK041(di)025:46: gnod byed 'byung po'i rigs rnams kyis //
NK041(di)025:47: bzung ba thong la bcing pa khrol //
NK041(di)025:48: bsdam pa klod la mnan pa khyogs //
NK041(di)025:49: gdon rnams gdug rtsub gnod 'tshe zhi //
NK041(di)025:50: byams pa'i sems dang ldan gyur te //
NK041(di)025:51: phan tshun bde la gnas par shog /
NK041(di)025:52: rkang gnyis khyed cag 'de legs shog /
NK041(di)025:53: rkang bzhi khyed cag bde legs shog /
NK041(di)025:54: skye dgu kun kyang bde legs shing //
NK041(di)025:56: tshe ring nad med dpal gyis brgyan //
NK041(di)025:57: rtag tu bde zhing don kun bsgrub //
NK041(di)025:58: chos dang ldan zhing byams la gnas //
NK041(di)025:59: thams cad sangs rgyas thob par shog /
